metadata.name: FLYC #1
metadata.description:
The Fly Now Space Club starts with a collection of 5 audiovisual arts and 119 one of a kind Astronaut NFT living on the Ethereum blockchain. Your Astronaut give you acess to the Space Club: a Community investing in life-changing cientific studys in space. FLYC holders have the power to shape our future projects and access to exclusive experiences, merch and more. Visit www.flynowspaceclub.com for more details.
“tothemoon” we mean it, we are actually going to the moon. Welcome to the mission.
